I wouldn't let go of the past♪

6
00:00:25,449 --> 00:00:32,666
♪It was just a habit
to cling to each moment♪

7
00:00:32,666 --> 00:00:36,265
=Captain Han=

8
00:00:36,265 --> 00:00:38,323
=Episode 22=

9
00:00:39,319 --> 00:00:40,200
Well,

10
00:00:40,919 --> 00:00:42,279
they're fine.

11
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:45,520
We're relieved.

12
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:54,479
Wu Wen, half a year ago,
you were Captain Han's love rival.

13
00:00:55,319 --> 00:00:57,159
How did you suddenly

14
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:58,560
become their love guardian?

15
00:01:01,759 --> 00:01:03,479
