16
00:01:04,839 --> 00:01:05,800
After everything,

17
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:06,959
I realized

18
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:10,279
what difficulties facing them.

19
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:14,279
Well,

20
00:01:14,919 --> 00:01:15,959
aren't you the same?

21
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,400
Yes.

22
00:01:21,199 --> 00:01:23,160
I heard when the police came,

23
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,720
