99
00:05:28,239 --> 00:05:30,016
Let's go.

100
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,936
Here.

101
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,080
Thank you.

102
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,320
Cheers, come on.

103
00:05:41,799 --> 00:05:43,160
What's going on with them?

104
00:05:43,679 --> 00:05:45,160
Something must be going on.

105
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,399
They're all here for the party.

106
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,440
Why haven't you come yet?

107
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,000
I haven't finished my report yet.

108
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,239
Are you drinking?

109
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,600
A bit.

110
00:05:53,119 --> 00:05:54,040
Send me the address.

111
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,320
I'll come to pick you up now.

112
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,640
Han Xizhou.

113
00:05:56,799 --> 00:05:58,079
Come on. I won't get drunk

114
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:00,200
