123
00:06:27,119 --> 00:06:29,320
No, just a bit.

124
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,279
Really?

125
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:34,320
Yes.

126
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:39,320
Nannan, I really missed you tonight.

127
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,399
But we saw each other in the daytime.

128
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,920
But you wasted so much time.

129
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:47,040
Let's go. They are waiting for us.

130
00:06:50,119 --> 00:06:51,519
Cheers.

131
00:07:18,559 --> 00:07:19,399
Han Xizhou.

132
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,399
I came back in a hurry,

133
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,920
